b'{"data_headers":{"result_code":1},"data":{"information":{"article_id":2054,"category_name":"Events","pr_category_id":"4","title_name":"Legend Difficulty Is Coming to Ciella\'s Wrath!","message":"<div>A new Legend difficulty will be added to Ciella&#39;s Wrath in The Agito Uprising (high-difficulty quests where you&#39;ll face powerful foes) on <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1616738400\\"><\/span>.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Ciella&#39;s Wrath: Legend may only be undertaken by a team of wind-attuned adventurers and dragons. Clear this quest to earn materials required to further refine wind-attuned 6\\u2605 weapons. Once an Agito weapon is refined to its second stage, its appearance will change!<\/div><div><br><\/div><div><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/1d5f53de89d3c0fe52db7a93bad92726.png\\"><\/div><div>The Agito despair before this cruel reality.<\/div><div>The Agito despair before putrid deception.<\/div><div>The Agito despair before false salvation.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>With a malicious sneer, the wings of contempt thrust those who profess false justice into the depths of misery and anguish. These wings that laugh derisively at such despair have a name, and that name is Ciella.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u25a0Changes to Survival Bonuses and the Number of Revives<\/div><div>Survival bonuses and the number of revives will change on <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1616738400\\"><\/span>. The number of revives in Ciella&#39;s Wrath: Master will be changed to one, and survival bonuses will be added. The number of revives in Ciella&#39;s Wrath: Expert will be increased to two, and the survival bonus content will be changed. The number of revives in Ciella&#39;s Wrath: Standard will be increased to three, and the survival bonus content will be changed.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Notes:<\/div><div>1. Players must have completed Chapter 10 \/ 6-3 (Normal) of the main campaign and any of the Standard-difficulty Advanced Dragon Trials in solo or co-op play to play The Agito Uprising.<\/div><div>2. Players must have completed Ciella&#39;s Wrath: Master in solo or co-op play to play Ciella&#39;s Wrath: Legend in solo play.<\/div><div>3. Players must have completed Ciella&#39;s Wrath: Master in solo or co-op play to play Ciella&#39;s Wrath: Legend in co-op play.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.<\/div>","start_time":1616133600,"prev_article_id":"2041","next_article_id":"2070","image_path":"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/1d5f53de89d3c0fe52db7a93bad92726.png","update_time":1616116879}}}'